OL,3,CRenewables overtake coal globally for
OL,4,Cfirst time on record ` analysis
OL,6,FThe world may be reaching a "crucial
OL,7,Fturning point" in the shift towards
OL,8,Fclean power, a think tank said as its
OL,9,Fanalysis showed renewable generation
OL,10,Fovertook coal globally for the first
OL,11,Ftime on record.
OL,13,FSolar and wind outpaced the growth in
OL,14,Fglobal electricity demand in the first
OL,15,Fhalf of 2025, according to Ember, a
OL,16,Fglobal energy research organisation.
