OL,3,CRenewables overtake coal globally for
OL,4,Cfirst time on record ` analysis
OL,6,FThe team analysed monthly electricity
OL,7,Fdata from 88 countries, representing
OL,8,F93% of global demand, and then
OL,9,Festimated changes in the remaining
OL,10,Fgeneration to form a worldwide picture.
OL,12,FIt found that renewables generated
OL,13,Fmore power than coal for the first
OL,14,Ftime, and that overall both coal and
OL,15,Fgas generation saw a slight decline
OL,16,Fglobally, compared to the first six
OL,17,Fmonths of 2024.
