OL,3,CRenewables overtake coal globally for
OL,4,Cfirst time on record ` analysis
OL,6,FMalgorzata Wiatros-Motyka, senior
OL,7,Felectricity analyst at Ember, said:
OL,8,F"We are seeing the first signs of a
OL,9,Fcrucial turning point.
OL,11,F"Solar and wind are now growing fast
OL,12,Fenough to meet the world's growing
OL,13,Fappetite for electricity.
OL,15,F"This marks the beginning of a shift
OL,16,Fwhere clean power is keeping pace with
OL,17,Fdemand growth."
