OL,3,CRenewables overtake coal globally for
OL,4,Cfirst time on record ` analysis
OL,6,FAs a result, Ember estimates that
OL,7,Fglobal power sector emissions fell by
OL,8,F0.2% in the first six months of 2025.
OL,10,FThe researchers said the drop is
OL,11,Fmodest but significant and that the
OL,12,Frise of renewables will likely
OL,13,Foutstrip demand growth for longer and
OL,14,Flonger periods.
OL,16,FIn terms of the four biggest
OL,17,Feconomies, China and India both saw
OL,18,Ffossil generation fall in the first
OL,19,Fhalf of 2025 as clean power growth
OL,20,Foutpaced demand.
