OL,4,Cfirst time on record ` analysis
OL,6,FBy contrast, fossil generation rose in
OL,7,Fthe US and the EU, with the former's
OL,8,Fdemand growth outpacing clean power
OL,9,Fand the latter seeing weaker wind and
OL,10,Fhyrdo output.
OL,12,FSonia Dunlop, chief executive of
OL,13,FGlobal Solar Council, said: "This
OL,14,Fanalysis confirms what we are
OL,15,Fwitnessing on the ground: solar and
OL,16,Fwind are no longer marginal
OL,17,Ftechnologies ` they are driving the
OL,18,Fglobal power system forward.
